<TEXT>
<P>
   Here is a listing of the New York Times News Service Macintosh
graphics files that moved Sunday, 05/23/99. Included is the
corresponding story slug and the size. All graphics have been
posted on PressLink, NewsCom and the Wieck Photo Database.
</P>
<P>
   MISSILE_How it works -- 38p6 x 6 -- MISSILE-DEFENSE
</P>
<P>
   APPEALS_Bold new court -- 2 x 7 -- APPEALS-COURT
</P>
<P>
   SPAIN_Aznalczar locator -- 1 x 3 -- SPAIN-POLLUTE
</P>
<P>
   CONGO_Kinshasa locator -- 1 x 2 1/4 -- CONGO-KABILA
</P>
<P>
   KOSOVO_Blace, Macedonia map -- 1 x 2 1/2 -- KOSOVO-MACEDONIA
</P>
<P>
   NEWSWEEK_Meacham at a glance -- 15p6 x 3 1/4 --
NEWSWEEK-MEACHAM-MEDIA
